Sun Yumeng, left, a 20-year-old fireman of three years and Wan Jingyan, right, a 26-year-old who was a nine-year veteran of the department, were also killed in the tragedy

But despite digging for four hours the three trapped firemen, along with the worker, were dead by the time they reached them.

The victims of the tragedy were named as Wan Jingyan, 26, a nine year veteran of the department, Sun Yumeng, 20, a fireman for three years, and their leader Liang, a ten year veteran.

'Firemen are the greatest people, and we saw that today,' said a newscaster on the local TV channel.'

